        <body>
      
		<pb n="1"/>
			<p rend="align(center)"><placeName>New York</placeName> <date>Shebat 17<hi rend="sup">th</hi> 5609</date></p>
			<p><addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
          <p rend="indent(1)"><placeName>Philada</placeName></p>  
          <p rend="indent(2)">Dear Sir</p>
          <p rend="indent(3)">In answer to yours I have to communicate<lb/> that I have another <add>Hebrew</add> on hand entirely new and<lb/> most Splendid written I may say better than the former<lb/> you have seen at the same amount &#36;75 or &#36;70. I have<lb/> also a new <add>Hebrew</add> in fact various&#44; from 16 to 12&#44; if you<lb/> know of Any <add>Hebrew</add> in want of the above named articles<lb/> please to name the parties or &#8220;<add>Hebrew</add>&#8221;</p>
			<p>The subject of which I wanted to meet you&#44; is<lb/> that &#8220;<add>Hebrew</add>&#8221; <persName>Mr Isidore Bush</persName> from <placeName><sic>Wienna</sic></placeName> is<lb/> residing here in town and calling on me&#44; as having<lb/> debt with him and having confidence in me&#44; his idea<lb/> being to commence or rather resume his printing estab&#45;<lb/>lishment here&#44; having a large apartment of Hebr. &#38; Germ.<lb/> types on hand&#44; there are more particulars concerned which<lb/> I cannot mention here&#44; if you might think proper<lb/> that anything can or could be done with us it would<lb/> to my opinions create much good to all parties&#44; and<lb/> would perhaps induce the American Israelites to procure<lb/> to their families many books&#44; not possessing at present.<lb/> <persName>Mr. I B</persName>&#59; having means to undertake the creation of<lb/> a new Establishment&#44; and I would be selected<lb/> by him as his <add>Hebrew</add> and salesman here ect.<lb/> &#8220;please to consider about it&#8221; most Respy Yours</p>
          <p rend="indent(6)"><persName role="author">Simon <add>&#63;</add></persName></p>
		<pb n="2"/>
			<p><addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
          <p rend="indent(1)"><placeName>Philada</placeName></p>
          <p rend="indent(2)"><placeName><hi rend="underline">Penn.</hi></placeName></p>

         
